<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-mast">
      <span class="eyebrow">Our Story</span>
      <h1>About Shanti Bryan Pinschers</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section container">
  <div class="split reveal">
    <div>
      <p>
        Shanti Bryan Pinschers is a small, home-based Miniature Pinscher kennel based in Bamenda,
        Cameroon. We breed in limited numbers, by design &mdash; every litter is whelped indoors,
        every puppy handled daily, and every parent dog screened for health and temperament
        before being bred.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px;">
        We keep a written record for each puppy: parentage, vaccination and deworming schedule,
        and any health notes from our vet. That record travels home with the puppy, alongside
        ongoing support if you have questions after pickup.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px;">
        We also run an active community of Min Pin owners and enthusiasts &mdash; if you already
        have a Shanti Bryan puppy, you're welcome there.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-photo-frame">
      <div style="aspect-ratio:4/5; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; color:var(--muted); background:var(--parchment-dark); font-size:13px;">
        Kennel photo
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section container" style="background:var(--card); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);">
  <div class="section-head reveal"><div><span class="eyebrow">What We Promise</span><h2>Our Standard of Care</h2></div></div>
  <div class="ledger-grid reveal-group">
    <div class="ledger-card"><div class="ledger-card-body">
      <h3>Health-Checked Parents</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:14px;">Both sire and dam are vet-checked before breeding, with attention to known breed health considerations.</p>
    </div></div>
    <div class="ledger-card"><div class="ledger-card-body">
      <h3>Raised In-Home</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:14px;">Puppies are whelped and weaned inside our home, not in a kennel building, and handled daily from birth.</p>
    </div></div>
    <div class="ledger-card"><div class="ledger-card-body">
      <h3>Full Documentation</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted); font-size:14px;">Every placement includes a written record of lineage, vaccinations, and deworming &mdash; referenced by ledger number.</p>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section container" style="text-align:center;">
  <h2>Have a question before you inquire?</h2>
  <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:14px;">Get in Touch</a>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
